**/.deprecated/**
**/archived/**
**/deprecated/**

# Backup files (deprioritize but don't exclude)
!deprioritize:**/*_backup.*,0.5
!deprioritize:**/*.bak,0.5
!deprioritize:**/*.old,0.5
!deprioritize:**/backup/**,0.3

